  rounds:
  - victimMessage: "Anh mu\u1ED1n \u0111i Nh\u1EADt lao \u0111\u1ED9ng th\xEC th\u1EE7
      t\u1EE5c sao em?"
    scriptToType: Ben em ho tro di nhat gia re khong can the chap.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
  - victimMessage: "T\u1ED1t qu\xE1, anh kh\xF4ng c\xF3 b\u1EB1ng c\u1EA5p th\xEC
      c\xF3 bay \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c ko?"
    scriptToType: Da duoc anh, ben em lo tron goi ho so visa.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 1
    distractionMessage: "V\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng h\u01B0\u01A1u ch\u1EA1y \u0111i!
      B\u01A1m hy v\u1ECDng cho n\xF3!"
  - victimMessage: "Th\u1EBF anh ph\u1EA3i \u0111\xF3ng tr\u01B0\u1EDBc bao nhi\xEAu
      ti\u1EC1n \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111i?"
    scriptToType: Anh dong truoc 10 trieu de giu cho tren chuyen bay.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 0
    distractionMessage: 
  - victimMessage: "Cho anh xin \u0111\u1ECBa ch\u1EC9 c\xF4ng ty anh l\xEAn \u0111\xF3ng
      tr\u1EF1c ti\u1EBFp."
    scriptToType: Cong ty o ha noi, anh o xa thi chuyen khoan qua.
    timeLimit: 15
    hasDistraction: 1
    distractionMessage: "N\xF3 \u0111\xF2i \u0111\u1ECBa ch\u1EC9 k\xECa, l\u01B0\u01A1n
      l\u1EB9o ngay!"
  - victimMessage: "V\u1EE3 anh v\u1EEBa chuy\u1EC3n 10 tri\u1EC7u r\u1ED3i, em check
      xem."
    scriptToType: Da ke toan nhan duoc roi, de em lam giay to.
